---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Sermon Series">
  <h1>Sermon Series</h1>

  <p>A sermon series groups multiple sermons under a shared arc. Each series has a title, description, optional date range, optional banner image, and a list of member sermons.</p>
  <h2>Authoring order</h2>
  <p>Create the series first, then add sermons to it (either by editing each sermon and selecting the series, or by dragging in the series detail view).</p>
  <h2>Public surface</h2>
  <p>Series get their own detail page at <code>/sermons/series/{slug}</code> with all member sermons listed in order.</p>
</BaseLayout>
